---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact — Meish"
  description="Tell us about your property or event and what you'd like guests to feel. We'll suggest the smallest first step — usually a single Meish Experience Signal Audit."
>
  <section class="section container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Start with one conversation.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Tell us about your property or event and what you'd like guests to feel.
      We'll suggest the smallest first step — usually a single Meish Experience Signal Audit.</p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p><a class="button button--primary" href="mailto:moona.m@meish.work?subject=Meish%20enquiry">Email moona.m@meish.work</a></p>
    <p>When you write, it helps to include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your property or organisation</li>
      <li>What you'd like guests to feel</li>
      <li>The best way to reach you</li>
    </ul>

    <p><small>A dedicated <code>hello@meish.work</code> address and an online booking link are
      coming soon.</small></p>
  </section>
</Base>
